<p class="ql-align-justify">童星出身，近年发展并不如意的曹骏：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201205/f25ba61ae13444bb83a867493ec3cf8e.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">在《三十而已》里面扮演小三的张月：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201205/ec6121dcea484389b15f5506826062ca.png" max-width="600" /></p>
